---
title: Smoky Paprika Shrimp & Rice Bowls with Bell Pepper & Lemon-Cilantro Sauce
description: Smoky paprika flavors succulent chicken thighs along with oregano and garlic powder for this easy weeknight rice bowl. The chicken cooks along with onion and bell pepper and is piled over steamy jasmine rice that soaks up all the flavors. A creamy lemon-cilantro sauce drizzled over top elevates this simple meal to new culinary heights!
